text: Peter Stocker (born 5 October 1956) is a Swiss rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Switzerland Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
